Animenu was written from 2001 - 2003 by Alastair M. Robinson.

OSD code very loosely based on code from wmix by timecop.

Thanks to Marimus for pointing out some bugs in both the code and
documentation.

Thanks to Kresimir Kukulj for increasing Animenu's flexibility with
command-line options.

Thanks to Massimo Maricchiolo for implementing the configuration file.

Thanks to Alexandar Belov for implementing the browse menu type.
